- A distinct `phrase_family` label
- Family-specific `transform_ops` merged (deduplicated) with section-level harmonic ops
- A `seed_phrase_id` back-reference (non-seed phrases point to the section's seed)

**`tests/test_fractal_form.py`** — 12 tests covering:
- Phrase-family slot grammar (count, seed-first, distinctness, padding)
- Phrase-family metadata presence for song/extended/suite trees
- Seed-derivation tracking (non-seed phrases reference the seed)
- Anti-looping (multi-phrase sections have distinct transform ops)
- Development/turn sections require >=2 distinct families
- Full macro→section→phrase→motif hierarchy verification
- JSON round-trip of new fields

